01:52:08.120 --> 01:52:10.079
Hello.

01:52:10.748 --> 01:52:14.459
I don't know whether you can hear me,
old Jacob Marley.

01:52:14.627 --> 01:52:19.214
And I don't know whether or not
I imagined the things I saw.

01:52:19.381 --> 01:52:21.799
But between the pair of us we...

01:52:21.967 --> 01:52:26.471
We finally made a Merry Christmas,
didn't we?

01:52:27.890 --> 01:52:29.891
I have to leave you now.

01:52:30.059 --> 01:52:32.310
Must go and get ready.

01:52:32.478 --> 01:52:37.190
I'm going to have Christmas dinner
with my family.

